{"commentv2": 1, "number": 17, "id": 299391, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "jlm97b", "body": "me and a 70 hunter went into his room and he is asleep, we couldn't aggro him....any ideas why??", "date": "2008-06-04T01:10:37-05:00", "rating": -3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "You need to kill the prophet (Jammal'an) first, which also spawns the green drakes (not sure if you need to kill these as well before Eranikus is attackable, since most appropriate level parties have to kill them to reach Eranikus anyway).", "creationdate": "2008-06-04T01:39:17-05:00", "id": 35423, "rating": 16, "commentid": 299391, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Auben", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 18, "id": 299612, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "YuriElite", "body": "Hardest low level instance boss ever!!!", "date": "2008-06-04T13:25:04-05:00", "rating": -3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "First time I did this we almost wiped cuz we didn't clear all the mobs but Divine Intervention saved our asses and and so I realized that we pallies aren't as useless.", "creationdate": "2008-07-07T00:54:03-05:00", "id": 340667, "rating": 0, "commentid": 299612, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Samad", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 19, "id": 323636, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "133226", "body": "Poor Eranikus has been nerfed, [i]HARD.[/i]\r\n\r\nHe used to be badass, used to be intimidating even to level 60s.\r\n\r\nNow he's a pushover. Indeed, the entire instance is.\r\n\r\nHit my paladin (Ret spec, ret gear, level 49) for 150 to 220.", "date": "2008-07-10T04:30:59-05:00", "rating": -3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
