{"commentv2": 1, "number": 42, "id": 2083835, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Pyrus42", "body": "Hold on, wasn't this guy purified during the AQ quest chain?", "date": "2015-01-06T19:26:15-06:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Yes he was. Also Stratholme was purified during classic, Molten Core was vanquished, The Scarlet Crusader had been slaughtered to the last, and yet they still keep coming back. Just because something happened once, does not mean it won't act like it never happened at all. MMOs are wierd like that.", "creationdate": "2015-01-08T13:05:44-06:00", "id": 825148, "rating": 3, "commentid": 2083835, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Skullhawk13", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Agreed, although I at least have an in-universe theory for this. Bronze dragons set up these as alternate areas to allow heroes to train themselves when they aren't ready to join the frontlines so they can gain some experience.", "creationdate": "2015-05-31T01:41:13-05:00", "id": 872546, "rating": 2, "commentid": 2083835, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Pyrus42", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
