{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 676397, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "rhinoloupe", "body": "Comment from [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=15491#comments]Eranikus, Tyrant of the Dream[/url]:\r\n\r\n[quote]Spawns during a part of the AQ opening quest line. He starts out flying over the lake, exchanging menacing words between the leaders of Moonglade. He spawns a plethora of shadow mobs that are devastatingly efficient in killing masses of guards. After all the shadow creatures are killed, Eranikus lands into Moonwell and begins to fight. Players struggle to kill him and heal the tank while Tyrande Whisperwind tries to help him overcome the evil inside him.\r\n\r\nWhen the battle is finished, he becomes Eranikus the Redeemed.[/quote]", "date": "2009-04-14T16:53:44-05:00", "rating": 7, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 6722, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Minorou", "body": "Spawns during a part of the AQ opening quest line.  He starts out flying over the lake, exchanging menacing words between the leaders of Moonglade.  He spawns a plethora of shadow mobs that are devastatingly efficient in killing masses of guards.  After all the shadow creatures are killed, Eranikus lands into Moonglade and begins to fight.  Players struggle to kill him and heal the tank while Tyrande Whisperwind tries to help him overcome the evil inside him.\n\nWhen the battle is finished, he becomes Eranikus the Redeemed.", "date": "2006-12-05T19:27:04-06:00", "rating": 43, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Don't bother trying to make it to your trainer to train during this event.. -Nameless 36 druid victim.", "creationdate": "2010-04-19T16:29:22-05:00", "id": 159752, "rating": 16, "commentid": 6722, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "twistedtwilight", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-01-04T13:17:30-06:00", 1, "Minorou"]}
