{"commentv2": 1, "number": 23, "id": 847321, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "111622", "body": "Can you kite him anywhere, or does Tyrande hold aggro?", "date": "2009-09-22T03:56:58-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "[s]Tyrande does not hold aggro at any point in the encounter.  She comes in once he gets to 20%, then you should get the quest complete.  As for if he can be kited, I would love if someone can give me information on that as well.[/s]  Just did it with my rogue's arena partner for around the 50th time in an attempt to kite him.  Eranikus is chained to one spot the entire fight and cannot be moved.  If it weren't for this minor detail, I can fully see you being able to kite him with a healer and a tank that are skilled kiters.    That said, looks like it's back to kiting Anachronos to Orgrimmar ", "creationdate": "2009-09-22T03:56:59-05:00", "id": 436077, "rating": 1, "commentid": 847321, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Sincloud", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 24, "id": 976998, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "StaticLgtBrngr", "body": "Moonglade [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?event=327]Lunar Festival[/url] event goers yesterday were surprised to discover that [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=15467]Omen[/url] was not the only thing attacking it.\r\n\r\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bYzqlpVIkeA", "date": "2010-02-15T09:51:50-06:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Lunar festival is great time to do this quest. No shortage of people around to help. And you can bet they'll know something's happening pretty soon after it starts.", "creationdate": "2010-04-25T19:22:59-05:00", "id": 160698, "rating": 2, "commentid": 976998, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "DrCheis", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 25, "id": 995481, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Rommon", "body": "Once you finish the quest, can you come back and summon him again anytime you like, or is it a one-off summon?", "date": "2010-03-11T13:37:11-06:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "The summon occurs when you accept the quest, so no, cannot be re-summoned after completing it.", "creationdate": "2010-04-25T19:23:35-05:00", "id": 160699, "rating": 1, "commentid": 995481, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "DrCheis", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
